, 207, 7); height: 31px; width: 480px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"http://pag.ae/bgvK833\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; touch-action: manipulation; color: rgb(92, 184, 92) !important;\">http://pag.ae/bgvK833</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"http://pag.ae/bcwr6cZ\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; touch-action: manipulation; color: rgb(92, 184, 92) !important;\">http://pag.ae/bcwr6cZ</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(55, 58, 60); font-size: 1.75rem;\">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(55, 58, 60); font-size: 1.75rem; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Para pagamentos via depósito ou transferência bancária, solicitar os dados para um administrador&nbsp;da liga ( Odirlei )</span></span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(55, 58, 60); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">Após o pagamento, por favor enviar uma foto do comprovante para administrador.</span></span></span></p>'),
